---
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section
  id="process"
  class="diagonal relative mt-20 flex w-screen flex-col items-center justify-center px-0 pb-36"
>
  <SectionTitle
    title1="What My"
    title2="Colleagues Say About Me..."
    class="mx-auto text-center"
    alternate={true}
  />
  <div
    class="grid-col mx-auto grid max-w-xs gap-12 sm:max-w-7xl sm:grid-cols-3 [&>div]:bg-designsystem-800/20"
  >
    <div class="rounded-sm bg-designsystem-800/20 p-12">
      <blockquote class="prose prose-lg font-syne text-white">
        <svg
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="h-12 w-12 text-designsystem-800/40"
          viewBox="0 0 24 27"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <path
            d="M14.017 18L14.017 10.609C14.017 4.905 17.748 1.039 23 0L23.995 2.151C21.563 3.068 20 5.789 20 8H24V18H14.017ZM0 18V10.609C0 4.905 3.748 1.038 9 0L9.996 2.151C7.563 3.068 6 5.789 6 8H9.983L9.983 18L0 18Z"
            fill="currentColor"></path>
        </svg>

        Iuliia excelled in her ability to understand and <b class="font-bold"
          >incorporate our business needs
        </b> into the design system. She ensured that every design system element
        was <b class="font-bold">consistent</b> and easy for our development team
        to implement, <b class="font-bold"
          >significantly improving our development times.
        </b>
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-200">- President of Britannica Home Fashions</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-sm bg-designsystem-800/20 p-12">
      <blockquote class="prose prose-lg font-syne text-white">
        <svg
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="h-12 w-12 text-designsystem-800/40"
          viewBox="0 0 24 27"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <path
            d="M14.017 18L14.017 10.609C14.017 4.905 17.748 1.039 23 0L23.995 2.151C21.563 3.068 20 5.789 20 8H24V18H14.017ZM0 18V10.609C0 4.905 3.748 1.038 9 0L9.996 2.151C7.563 3.068 6 5.789 6 8H9.983L9.983 18L0 18Z"
            fill="currentColor"></path>
        </svg>

        Iuliia has the <b class="font-bold">innovative spirit</b>needed in the
        UX design field. With a <b class="font-bold">strategic mind</b> that comes
        from her MBA studies and experience, and a <b class="font-bold"
          >keen design sense</b
        >, what I liked most about Iuliia's work is the creativity in design.
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-200">- UX Design Manager</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-sm bg-designsystem-800/20 p-12">
      <blockquote class="prose prose-lg font-syne text-white">
        <svg
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="h-12 w-12 text-designsystem-800/40"
          viewBox="0 0 24 27"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        >
          <path
            d="M14.017 18L14.017 10.609C14.017 4.905 17.748 1.039 23 0L23.995 2.151C21.563 3.068 20 5.789 20 8H24V18H14.017ZM0 18V10.609C0 4.905 3.748 1.038 9 0L9.996 2.151C7.563 3.068 6 5.789 6 8H9.983L9.983 18L0 18Z"
            fill="currentColor"></path>
        </svg>

        Iuliia excelled in her ability to understand and <b class="font-bold"
          >incorporate our business needs
        </b> into the design system. She ensured that every design system element
        was <b class="font-bold">consistent</b> and easy for our development team
        to implement, <b class="font-bold"
          >significantly improving our development times.
        </b>
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-200">- Sales and Marketing Executive</p>
    </div>
